要求来决定，","box":[[51,887],[618,886],[618,903],[51,904]]},{"text":"这是商品生产的特点之一。","box":[[68,918],[335,918],[335,937],[68,937]]},{"text":"99","box":[[584,994],[608,994],[608,1012],[584,1012]]}],"dimensions":{"height":1060,"width":709}}